n所謂靚衫，特別係突顯女性身材體態或者性感衣著<br />\n以至女性身材上嘅審美觀<br />\n向來都係基於「因為男人鍾意」而設定出嚟<br />\n婦團可以否認㗎，但係歸根究底<br />\n女裝嗰啲貼身/暴露嘅衫嘅設計原意係咩<br />\n其實大家心知肚明啦<br />\n又唔見港女之間會流行包到密密實實、闊袍大袖嘅衣著<br />\n所謂嘅唔好睇，講到尾係指男人覺得唔好睇咋<br />\n<br />\n所以，設計旗袍嗰個人就算唔係淫棍<br />\n都一定會了解男人官能上嘅喜好"},{"pid":"13c240a0c480207885df394a9ddecac910acd474","tid":527120,"uid":115354,"like":85,"dislike":1,"score":84,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a22b653b783f6fb09e6a0a8fd2e57b78cbe15e94","tid":527120,"uid":115354,"like":57,"dislike":7,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:06:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe0e7e6b12b6642c4aad03573d53ef7b29bf5a4","tid":527120,"uid":115354,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117de05f3925cae67b3898e004756df9f17be676","tid":527120,"uid":115354,"like":49,"dislike":4,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322fe86265b65e72026892a97fee08a755276ee0","tid":527120,"uid":115354,"like":25,"dislike":45,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:09:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c058281ecd7405a561d885c1b19a55461542f63","tid":527120,"uid":84619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d64779f11ec80b89976fed712092e2eb45e6229a","tid":527120,"uid":153316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"419303101c2937260c07d0c3a547207349dfa08c","tid":527120,"uid":57297,"like":305,"dislike":3,"score":302,"quote":{"pid":"6902900c1d15e40b2bf87c3f5f94c7beccc73b5f","tid":527120,"uid":23818,"like":167,"dislike":1,"score":166,"qu